full_text: Screened by NARA, 6/1/2023 FIRST WISCONSIN NATIONAL BANK WS of Milwaukee AUDITING DEPARTMENT August 15, 1969 Mr. Perfecto Gonzalez or FOIA (b)(6) 2250 North 16th Street Milwaukee, Wisconsin 53205 Dear Messrs. Gonzalez: This is to certify that the balance on the books of the First Wisconsin National Bank of Milwaukee, Wisconsin to the credit of Perfecto or FOIA (b)(6) as of the close of business August 14, 1969 was: $3,575.47 in Saving Account number 1302707 at our Fond du Lac at North Office. This account opened May 5, 1967. Very truly yours, J. G. Anderson Assistant Auditor Subscribed and sworn to before me a Notary Public this fifteenth day of August, 1969. Eik has NOTARY PUBLIC, MILWAUKEE COUNTY, WISCONSIN E. H. FREY Notary Public Milwaukea County, Wisconsin My Commission Expires April 18, 1971 SEAL eln 743 NORTH WATER STREET .
